--><lb
n="10"/>Ātma-navamāya mātrāḍhyāryyāya
da<choice><sic>ttā</sic><corr>tto</corr></choice> yata EteṣāM brāhmaṇā<supplied reason="omitted">nā</supplied><sic>M</sic> vi<!--
